node.text:
Hey everybody,
Do you ever find yourself stuck in the middle? Not cold, not hot; just Lukewarm? We’re excited to announce the anticipated release of the movie SELHO. This movie was created by the youth of St.George Coptic Orthodox Church targeting the theme of lukewarmness commonly found within the Christian community. The youth of St. George has worked on this project for the past three years and would love for you to finally see it!
To watch this film, just complete a brief 20 second survey and the link for the film will be in your survey confirmation. Start by just clicking on the link in our bio
All proceeds/donations made will serve nonprofits (St. George and @Jesus_the_Lord_). We really appreciate your contributions and hope you enjoy!
For any additional questions/comments, feel free to contact johneshak@ymail.com

node.text: God has you in the palm of His hand and He promises that He will protect you and your family from the evil one! Psalm 139 tells us that God goes before us, behind us, beside us, and He places His hand of blessing upon our heads! I want you to believe and receive what I am about to say. If you can, say this aloud. “I am the child of the King who is not moved by the world for my God is with me and goes before me. I do not fear because I am His!” God has also COMMANDED His angels to guard you in all your ways! So go to sleep tonight in peace, knowing that God, the Creator of the heavens and the earth and everything in it, is in control and is still on His throne! Your Heavenly Father will most definitely protect you and your family tonight and always. Sweet dreams, beloved. ❤️
